description:
In 1873, The North-West Mounted Police was established in an attempt to bring order to the chaos of The Canadian Frontier, a lawless place where man and myth clashed and the old world repulsed the new.

The mightiest among the N.W.M.P. was Sam Steele, and expert horseman, marksmen, and leader of men.

These are his legendary adventures.
name: Dead Horse Trail
